data.actual_result: White circle obviously can't be seen on white background which is because of incorrectly themed white circle.
data.short_description: The white circle behind the # in the list of text channels is incorrectly themed hence invisible in white theme.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to any text channel and type #. Notice list of channels popping up. - See there's a white circle behind the "#" before channel name. - Switch to white theme, and type # in any text channel and try to notice that circle
